# Battersea Chapel Database Backup Cron Job
# This file contains the cron job configuration for automated database backups
# 
# To install this cron job, run:
# crontab -e
# 
# Then add the following line:

# Daily backup at 2:00 AM
0 2 * * * /var/www/bchapel3/backup-db.sh

# Alternative schedules (uncomment one if you prefer different timing):
# 
# Every 6 hours:
# 0 */6 * * * /var/www/bchapel3/backup-db.sh
#
# Twice daily (2 AM and 2 PM):
# 0 2,14 * * * /var/www/bchapel3/backup-db.sh
#
# Weekly on Sunday at 3 AM:
# 0 3 * * 0 /var/www/bchapel3/backup-db.sh

# Note: Make sure the script is executable:
# chmod +x /var/www/bchapel3/backup-db.sh